articles.author: Zoe Phillips
articles.title: Travis Kelce Will Be in Argentina for Taylor Swift's Eras Tour Stop - Entertainment Tonight
articles.description: Taylor Swift begins the South America leg of her Eras Tour on Nov. 9 in Argentina.
articles.content:
Love seems to know no borders. ET has learned that Kansas City Chiefs tight end Travis Kelce is headed south of the equator for the start of Taylor Swift's South America leg of her Eras Tour.
